 research, A. M. Sperber reveals the complexity and achievements of a man whose voice, intelligence, and honesty inspired a nation during its most profound and vulnerable times.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Apr 2024) 7aBIOGRAPHY & AUTOBIOGRAPHY / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertFordham University Press Complete eBook-Package Pre-2014z978311118960408iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertFordham University Press eBook-Package Archive Pre-2000z97831107432960 cprintz978082321882040uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978082329625540uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780823296255423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780823296255/original  a978-3-11-074329-6  Fordham University Press eBook-Package Archive Pre-2000b2000  a978-3-11-118960-4  Fordham University Press Complete eBook-Package Pre-2014b2014  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_LT  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles